The paper deals with formal control synthesis approaches over stochastic systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of symbolic abstractions and the curse of dimensionality are also common themes in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also mentions the coordination of traffic lights, which is a topic in multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and robotics (cs.RO).
